{"tid":1668464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瘋警嘲勇武鄉音婦返大陸 被反譏：返屋企嗌你老母除褲","createTime":"2019-10-22T04:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T05:18:46.000Z","uid":68738,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d758b1a4ca08cef22007a9cc2cfcdf996010f45","tid":1668464,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191022/large/1571679447_8298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571679447_8298.jpg&h=f9ac8bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7.21元朗恐襲3個月，市民在元朗一帶聚集紀念，晚上有抗爭者堵路，警方一改7.21的做法，沒有掉頭離開找「增援」；也沒有接到報案後39分鐘才到達，而是第一時間派出大批防暴警到場驅散，更拖出警犬到場。<br />\n<br />\n有街坊裝束的市民，見警犬沒有戴口罩或防毒面具，於是提醒警員不要帶犬隻到放催淚彈的現場，卻反被警員粗言相向。又因街坊有口音，疑遭警歧視為內地新移民：「話我講嘢講得唔正啦，話我係大陸人啦：『你返大陸啦！』」街坊又指警查她身份證，她不禁怒從心起：「我嚟香港廿年喇，仆佢個街，歧視我哋啦，跟住佢X老母嘛，我話老母你哋返屋企X，你慢慢返屋企嗌你老母除咗褲畀你X。」<br />\n<br />\n街坊指，自己僅因叫警員不要帶警犬出來，「我話你有豬嘴戴，人哋狗仔冇豬嘴戴。」她指自己家中都養狗，質問警員帶犬出來做甚麼。不料警員竟回答：「狗唔帶佢落呢度，唔通帶佢去遊樂場玩丫？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191022/60180462?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60180462%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSAX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=fe99a49f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60180462%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=2055121e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191022/60180462?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4891a18307da4d7167346f6fb6a6a49d5a275931","tid":1668464,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:11:58.000Z","msg":"當所有生物係工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716f1e685df2a4bbf6b6ded735b35a59ea5cf421","tid":1668464,"uid":165525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"搵愛協溝通下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}